# Also ignored at the repo root, but the Tauri CLI's frontend-dir walker runs
# with parents(false) — it only reads ignore files inside the walked tree. The
# CI-vendored package.json beside bin/pi otherwise wins frontend detection, and
# beforeBuildCommand's `npm --prefix ../web` then resolves to vendor/web.
# Resource bundling is unaffected (plain glob, not gitignore-aware).
vendor/
